{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2439460/extras/follow_eng.gif?t=1727968155\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">TURI KAAPORA is a top-down Hack n' Slash action and adventure game, inspired by the Tupi - Guarani Indigenous culture. </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play as <strong>Caipora</strong> and fight with the fury of enchanted animals that will transform your blows and improve yourself with the help of ancestral indigenous entities and instruments. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Defend the Atlantic Forest from invaders and become the guardian of Nhe'ery!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2439460/extras/steam1.png?t=1727968155\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The fight is all yours:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As Kaapora you are tasked with expelling the men and machines that devastate the forest. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You will have enchanted weapons and a customizable headdress, so you can fight with blows in your own style. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Restore balance:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Help beings affected by human greed. With the help of elemental powers and spiritual entities, restore the forest, rescue the animals and do not let an invader remain on this land.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2439460/extras/steam2.png?t=1727968155\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Discover what is hidden:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Corrupted machines and elements have become enemies, wielders of maximum destruction. In the middle of the Atlantic Forest, there are secrets to be revealed and forces that can help in the fight.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_pa